name: Server Intellect
tag_list: hosting-solutions, cloud-servers, cloud-hosting, managed-services, public-cloud, private-cloud, dedicated-servers, windows-hosting, microsoft-hosting, microsoft-partner
overview:
Server Intellect assists businesses of all sizes around the world with their hosting needs by providing fully configured solutions coupled ServiceFirst Support™ - available 24x7x365.

Offerings include cloud hosting, cloud servers and dedicated servers and all technicians are Microsoft Certified through the Microsoft Certified Technology Specialization.

The Hosting Solutions meet your specific needs - whether it’s a single server, or a complex load-balanced configuration. Managed Services are also part of Server Intellect’s offerings, including email, disaster recovery, security, and many other options - all scalable to fit your business and grow with its needs.

Server Intellect is a member of the Microsoft Service Provider Licensing Agreement program and a Microsoft Gold Certified Partner.
